    "7303601": {
        "Desc": "Follow Arama into \"Old Vanarana\"",
        "Step": "The Ashvattha Tree has been corroded. But from its fruit, Arama seems to have gained new knowledge, memories, and... manners of speech. According to Arama, you should eliminate Marana's Avatar next so that the new Ashvattha Tree may be born. Only then can the Bija be formed.",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "*huff*... *huff*... You're flying too fast, Arama!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "Is that so? Sorry. But based on how you float, you shouldn't be exhausting any stamina."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon must be fully focused to fly, so it is exhausting! Arama, just fly at the speed of a Seelie, alright?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "A Seelie? In the ancient stories, Seelies were a great race with wisdom and beauty beyond the pale of this earth. They traveled with Nara and taught Nara languages and the philosophy of nature."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh? Paimon thought that they were just large but annoying fireflies that lead us around by the nose..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "Seelies are just empty husks that race left behind. This is because they were born with a curse: If they fall in love with Nara, they shall lose their intelligence and strength, and their bodies will regress."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "There was once a survivor of that race deep within the golden desert who was friends with Queen Aranyani and the ruler of Valuka. Perhaps there are more stories to be found in the eternal oasis."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmmm..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Anyway, don't fly too fast..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Anyway, Seelie annoy me..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "...Is there a reason why you told us that story?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "Yes. So you see... at their prime, the Seelies were probably faster than a storm. Plus, isn't Paimon tired? We can rest while I tell stories about Sarva."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "You even know how to be evasive now, Arama. You've really changed..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "Anyway, this was our first home{RUBY#[S]Vanarana}land. Aranara used to live here before the disaster, and many Nara had visited us."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Before the disaster... Are you saying that..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "Yes, and you've been to the second Vanarana. Meanwhile, Marana's Avatar is imprisoned by three seals deep within this place."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "Three Inscriptions of Remembrance are needed to undo the first seal. While the landscape here is a little different from the memories I received, I have a rough idea where they are."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "#Anyway, Marana is very dangerous. Nara {NICKNAME}, Paimon, I recommend we match each other's pace. Let me know when you're ready to set out."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Three seals, and we must find three Inscriptions of Remembrance just for the first seal... This is so troublesome. Why does everything have to be done three times?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "They don't call it \"The Rule of Three\" for nothing..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yeah... If Ruu were here, Paimon's sure he and Arama would become friends real quick..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "Ruu?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yes, he's a friend of ours."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "#I see. I too wish to meet Nara {NICKNAME} and Paimon's friend. A Nara who's friends with both of you is for sure a great Nara."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "But it's alright. The past and the future meet in Sarva. A day will come when I'll have the honor of meeting this Ruu and becoming friends with him."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "By the way, there are actually four seals imprisoning Marana. The first seal is the Door of Vana, which is right behind us."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Let's go."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yeah! It feels like we have so much to do! Let's get moving!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Yeah, let's go."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Let's rest a while longer..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "Alright. We'll set out whenever you are ready."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I wanna rest a while longer..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Arama",
                    "T": "Alright. We'll set out whenever you are ready."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
